FontBox

Packages
org.fontbox.afm This package holds classes used to parse AFM(Adobe Font Metrics) files.
org.fontbox.cmap This package holds classes that are necessary to parse cmap files.
org.fontbox.encoding This package contains the implementations for all of the encodings that are used in PDF documents.
org.fontbox.pfb Classes that are used to parse pfb files.
org.fontbox.ttf This package contains classes to parse a TTF file.
org.fontbox.util This package contains utility classes used by various font types.
